Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.88,0:00:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香 我肚子饿扁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.64,0:00:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.94,0:00:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在小心开车 别啰嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.44,0:00:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 比乌龟还要慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.05,0:00:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香 你在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.22,0:00:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使我稍微跟你开玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.40,0:00:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不要这么乱来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.88,0:00:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,减速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.20,0:00:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.09,0:00:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停车!!停车!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.83,0:00:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人!你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.51,0:00:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.24,0:00:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.38,0:00:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\fs45\shad3\4a&H00&}第五话 燃烧!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.04,0:01:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人 没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.00,0:01:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.49,0:01:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.52,0:01:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好点了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.56,0:01:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.80,0:01:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.16,0:01:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我撞车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.55,0:01:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没大碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.91,0:01:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.24,0:01:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然会撞车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.24,0:01:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我在郊外的单程路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.44,0:01:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车被超了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.72,0:01:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心情也非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.31,0:01:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不自觉地就猛力踏着油门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.60,0:01:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 就在那时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.15,0:01:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车好像突然变得很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.80,0:01:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直像开动了推进器一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.19,0:02:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你驾驶的是我们的GTO吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.99,0:02:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.07,0:02:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连600公里都不怕 GTO的速度你怎么会怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.20,0:02:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道 那只是我当时的错觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.06,0:02:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为撞车后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.76,0:02:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发现车速连30公里也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.29,0:02:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.28,0:02:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种饮料 你也喝了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.20,0:02:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的饮料是指...那些?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.45,0:02:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.80,0:02:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就可以肯定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.28,0:02:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种饮料有古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.01,0:02:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查它的成分好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.91,0:02:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.21,0:02:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放在修理站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.39,0:02:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我想反正是在比赛时喝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我房间应该还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我没喝完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.99,0:02:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.07,0:02:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那是我料想中的东西的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵就会大祸临头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.90,0:03:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.38,0:03:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在菲尔的车屋里找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.05,0:03:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多不胜数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.39,0:03:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.87,0:03:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预赛第三组是由经验丰富的选手互相比拚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.37,0:03:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\pos(504,525)}{\fs52.5}汉福国家公园\N{\fs42}丽湖乘船观光行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失落之环的选手奋力向前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.15,0:03:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒特洛杰怎么了? 选手们都不合拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.93,0:03:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们划得好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.37,0:03:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别输给美国人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.38,0:03:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!你们在做什么!美国男儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子连总统看了都会很失望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.45,0:03:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年一度的队际联谊赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年是举行划艇比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.30,0:03:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在水上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.10,0:03:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是比速度哪个车队都不想落败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.02,0:03:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他们不像平日般可以换胎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.59,0:03:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒特洛杰偏向右边 转弯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.78,0:03:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.91,0:03:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果现在输了他们今天就要由选手变为观众了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.84,0:04:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个车队无论如何都显示出决心和合作精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.81,0:04:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道原来有这种比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.30,0:04:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想趁机也加倍锻练下我们的员工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为赢了划艇或网球赛没什么意义吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.66,0:04:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 只要是比赛就要赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.44,0:04:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢不了就没意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.65,0:04:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡事都一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.58,0:04:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能过个快乐的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.58,0:04:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.62,0:04:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是那么打算的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论发生什么事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.54,0:04:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那果然好像是关于神经系统的新药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神经系统的新药?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.71,0:04:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之 它有两种功效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.96,0:04:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其一是对神经产生作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要是提升神经的传达速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.56,0:04:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令反射变得过于敏捷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.94,0:05:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一种是令脑部识别速度的中枢受到影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.52,0:05:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,产生意识上的麻痹状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换言之 喝了这种药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.98,0:05:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筋肉的反应速度会比平时快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也会失去对速度的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.11,0:05:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使开达数百公里速度也不会害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.73,0:05:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次果然事态严重呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.53,0:05:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我当时只是开到30公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.77,0:05:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像数百公里一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.72,0:05:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是药力失效时的反弹现象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.92,0:05:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当身体即将回复正常时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.43,0:05:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就会出现这样的副作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就完全明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前说过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是改变导航计算机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.09,0:05:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车手就能变成超人  当老板就不用那么辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.65,0:05:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕这就是答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.60,0:05:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.63,0:05:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.56,0:05:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在利用药物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.99,0:06:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是那样还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.85,0:06:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使失去对速度的恐惧也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应速度加快也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.00,0:06:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛里最重要的始终是车手自己的判断和技术吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.20,0:06:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为并非车手自己一个人在比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.44,0:06:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手 驾驶策略和赛道的情况也会不断改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他身为新人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.00,0:06:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却那么冷静 准确和毫无差错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.80,0:06:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只靠这种药的功效 他不可能有那种表现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.43,0:06:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 到底是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.65,0:06:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这只是推测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.60,0:06:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但生化计算机说不定能做到了解情况并因应变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.55,0:06:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择进入第几档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里加速  如何转弯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.46,0:06:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全由计算机决定 然后变成电脉冲波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传入车手体内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这只不过是我的推测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.87,0:07:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不那样解释的话就说不通了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.87,0:07:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的表现 还有这种药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.59,0:07:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种药大概会强迫车手的身体服从计算机的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说不是那家伙在比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是被计算机控制着进行比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.52,0:07:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.60,0:07:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预赛最后一组联合车队对菅生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.54,0:07:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...先进科技主导一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.12,0:07:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管多么想取胜也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.85,0:07:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.43,0:07:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事迹败露的话 葵就完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难逃被吊销牌照的厄运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.71,0:08:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你不知情也难以幸免
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.19,0:08:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.75,0:08:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然对不起今日子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.50,0:08:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我要向Ficcy投诉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.23,0:08:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到和那种家伙在同一赛道上比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 风见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.78,0:08:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能置之不理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.86,0:08:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.33,0:08:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.99,0:08:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.24,0:08:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你暂时把这件事交给我处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为...这是我们葵的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香小姐 我也求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.26,0:08:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你要快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.30,0:08:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种药不可能对身体无害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.05,0:08:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过度的负担会侵蚀神经组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,严重损害他的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.07,0:08:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样下去的话 他迟早会连性命都赔上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.44,0:08:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.53,0:09:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使他们知道会有那样的后果也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.26,0:09:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.87,0:09:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿烤好的给大家吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.73,0:09:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是风见先生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.10,0:09:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良平先生他们的是那碟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.26,0:09:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 风见先生哪去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.94,0:09:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才开始就一直没看到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了划艇比赛也没怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果赛车场上赢不了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.51,0:09:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每年都说一样的话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.15,0:09:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.46,0:09:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗利兹 Come On
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.58,0:09:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come Here
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.38,0:09:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.41,0:09:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙真害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.39,0:09:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是讨厌嘈杂的环境吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.77,0:10:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.99,0:10:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.71,0:10:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.60,0:10:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想问你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.08,0:10:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能赢就什么也不在乎吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.58,0:10:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你参赛的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜利用药物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.66,0:10:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被计算机操纵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使那样也好 只要能赢就可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.06,0:10:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那样也算车手吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.98,0:10:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不凭自己的力量去比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.44,0:10:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种胜利有什么意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.47,0:10:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛里 胜利就是一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.75,0:10:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落败就一无所有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光荣和未来也就没有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.29,0:10:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那全是胜利者所有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.58,0:11:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果你不能凭借自己的力量比赛\N那么胜利就毫无意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛里 胜利不是一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.26,0:11:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个幸福的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.09,0:11:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界冠军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.21,0:11:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连真正败北的意思也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.40,0:11:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神是不公平的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.54,0:11:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有力量的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.99,0:11:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白没有力量的人的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.09,0:11:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就连车手的尊严也抛弃吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认为你会明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.03,0:11:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会要你明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.85,0:11:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也有人不舍弃一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能抓紧唯一的光荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.86,0:11:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.61,0:11:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗利兹 隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.67,0:11:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗利兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.49,0:12:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.44,0:12:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己也应该知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.57,0:12:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样继续下去 你的身体会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.19,0:12:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有危险是意料中的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.41,0:12:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不惜断送性命吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.75,0:12:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.43,0:12:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.21,0:12:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向我伸出手的原来是恶魔吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.68,0:12:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗利兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.66,0:12:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不要紧 被选中的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.16,0:12:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做选择的也是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.67,0:12:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我一定会抓紧给你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.79,0:12:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧未来和光荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你们击败之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.58,0:12:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗利兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.63,0:12:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{}东京葵总公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.09,0:13:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最近看来很忙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.40,0:13:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很没礼貌呢 连门都不敲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.38,0:13:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有啊 但你没有回应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.44,0:13:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你在调查AL-ZARD吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.52,0:13:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是...我有点兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.71,0:13:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么说 那么出色的跑车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.97,0:13:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你跟我说就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.01,0:13:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们又不是敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.56,0:13:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你那么忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.71,0:13:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是你的要求  我什么都会答应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.25,0:13:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.31,0:13:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AL-ZARD的资料有很多是高度机密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道密码就什么也查不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.33,0:14:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来直接问你会比较好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.19,0:14:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到事情会发展成那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.32,0:14:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今你还狡辩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.67,0:14:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.70,0:14:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是你就相信了他的话来作多次调查吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.18,0:14:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 如果那样你才安心的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.66,0:14:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不介意你调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.13,0:14:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这件事或许更有蹊跷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更蹊跷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.00,0:14:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为菲尔和AL-ZARD的出现赛车变得没趣了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对加贺来说是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对菅生的风见隼人来说也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.05,0:14:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许没有比菲尔在赛场上消失来得更高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两人是好朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.96,0:15:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有车手间难得能建立友情是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.68,0:15:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那或许会变为仇恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.02,0:15:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当自己不断吃苦头的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.54,0:15:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事谨慎点比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.69,0:15:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果哪天你在众人面前出丑的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.28,0:15:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令尊不是会有麻烦吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.65,0:15:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是放不下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.24,0:15:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是弗利兹的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.92,0:15:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.83,0:16:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不惜那样也想赢比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.99,0:16:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人你不也是那样想过吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.58,0:16:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果心想输了也不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.92,0:16:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加比赛就没意义了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.82,0:16:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我是喜欢赛车才参赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.68,0:16:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在赛车场上比拼 尝过胜与败的滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.51,0:16:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非只是为了最先迎接格子旗的挥动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.89,0:16:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格子旗是车手凭自己力量取胜的证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.66,0:16:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.32,0:16:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那家伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.19,0:16:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂不是等于跑车的零件吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了最近的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有点害怕起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科技不断进步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.32,0:16:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑车不断变得更快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.19,0:16:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果跑车继续这样进化的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.00,0:17:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类或许有一天会跟不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.82,0:17:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.39,0:17:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛车真复杂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.63,0:17:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为跑车快就能赢是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.99,0:17:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使像新条和隼人你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.53,0:17:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直认为比赛是靠身为车手的自己也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.14,0:17:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不配合跑车进化的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.19,0:17:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就不能取胜对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.27,0:17:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 你生气了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香的话没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.88,0:17:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也非常想得到快的跑车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.06,0:17:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也尝试改用了花环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.36,0:17:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不是那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.34,0:17:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.18,0:17:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然只想有快的车就能赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.52,0:17:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我参赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.63,0:17:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是车和车手的并肩作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.80,0:18:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.79,0:18:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负不是问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.82,0:18:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你的拍檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使不是在比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.01,0:18:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是你的拍檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.55,0:18:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人 我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错 阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.26,0:18:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「他」一定在生气呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.49,0:18:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身为拍档却一直没有理「他」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.69,0:18:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「他」或许知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.85,0:18:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一样的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.74,0:19:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.20,0:19:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(504,525)\fs48}日本菅生试车场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.09,0:19:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.69,0:19:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候你说什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我任性 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.04,0:19:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我并非在开玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.29,0:19:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事?干嘛那么大声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.96,0:19:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也来斥责他一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.50,0:19:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个笨蛋竟然想现在用阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.30,0:19:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 克蕾雅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.20,0:19:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老是自作主张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.60,0:19:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.70,0:19:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.92,0:19:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我的花环不满吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.40,0:19:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克蕾雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的!克蕾雅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.44,0:19:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我不断地叫你耐心等待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.64,0:19:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说阿斯拉达已经落伍的人是隼人你唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.84,0:20:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你现在又说它比花环还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.12,0:20:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.94,0:20:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是那个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对花环没有不满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.79,0:20:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全没那意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呀 隼人 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.32,0:20:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...怎么说才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.27,0:20:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达对我来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.98,0:20:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和其它跑车不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.35,0:20:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它毕竟是我的拍档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.72,0:20:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人 习惯了的跑车比较好的说法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.17,0:20:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在比赛里是没有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.30,0:20:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是那意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.61,0:20:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过这次驾驶过花环后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.69,0:20:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发觉了一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.33,0:20:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我驾驶阿斯拉达时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.62,0:20:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直觉得是理所当然而没发觉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.67,0:20:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.60,0:20:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,例如 我想做一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.66,0:20:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花环当然能一下子做出我心目中要它做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.83,0:20:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而即使在任何时候和做多少次它也不会有改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.77,0:21:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是阿斯拉有点不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.76,0:21:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会在行进的过程中逐渐改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.52,0:21:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然那是因为我在改变的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.19,0:21:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但阿斯拉达能配合不断改变的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不只是服从我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.47,0:21:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然也不是要我服从它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.37,0:21:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达是以它自己的方式在比赛里思考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.97,0:21:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我并肩作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.87,0:21:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...所以我想借助它的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.54,0:21:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢得冠军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.80,0:21:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了赢AL-ZARD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.86,0:21:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.11,0:22:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.08,0:22:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45}ν-阿斯拉达AKF-0
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.64,0:22:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在驾驶舱的是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.81,0:22:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我 阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.77,0:22:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出所料 果然又是你吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.17,0:22:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登记为我唯一驾驶员的风见隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.60,0:22:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像不高兴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.88,0:22:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.60,0:22:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「你」?「你」是指我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.74,0:22:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我又没说不高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.45,0:22:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要安全系统没被解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.58,0:22:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正能开动我的只有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.98,0:22:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「反正」!?你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.07,0:22:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是太阳吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.85,0:22:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来还存在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.97,0:23:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得很久没见过太阳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.22,0:23:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我抛下你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.81,0:23:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样?隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.20,0:23:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修哥 这家伙的性格变了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.18,0:23:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它一直由克蕾雅照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.92,0:23:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 别说那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.85,0:23:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真的想用阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.28,0:23:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就要先和我比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.52,0:23:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑5圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.24,0:23:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你赢不了我的花环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.78,0:23:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在比赛里也只会成为笑柄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.19,0:23:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.14,0:23:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看来退化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.90,0:23:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.91,0:23:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是很久没合作迟钝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.33,0:23:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!Air Mode
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.82,0:23:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解 Air Mode
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.96,0:23:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达会赢对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.48,0:24:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看过才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.05,0:24:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然车型几乎相等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.08,0:24:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但阿斯拉达装了变型系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.37,0:24:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车身比较重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.06,0:24:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次真的要看隼人的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.86,0:24:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!转弯的技术仍是那么厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.50,0:24:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定风翼形状转为第二类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.40,0:24:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用惯性滑行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.00,0:24:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.99,0:24:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么 隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.17,0:24:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显示出你的决心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.94,0:24:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.68,0:24:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.04,0:24:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你的惯性滑行已经了如指掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.43,0:24:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有车手也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:55.36,0:24:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故意为难他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.77,0:24:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果赢不了修哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.22,0:25:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在比赛里的确…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.07,0:25:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.93,0:25:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下一个弯角用双重惯性滑行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.37,0:25:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支持我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.41,0:25:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.46,0:25:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转入内档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.73,0:25:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.37,0:25:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行!隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.40,0:25:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:36.91,0:25:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?跑车凌空转弯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.07,0:25:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...刚才做了什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:46.91,0:25:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:49.14,0:25:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来成功过头但弄错程序了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.86,0:25:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄错…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:54.36,0:25:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为计算机的你会弄错？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.81,0:25:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「懂游泳的也会溺死」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:02.74,0:26:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的并不是在说笑话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.52,0:26:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谚语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.87,0:26:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要笑成那样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.64,0:26:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.62,0:26:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那是你的厉害之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:12.78,0:26:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区谚语我还知道很多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:15.65,0:26:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是比赛时别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.31,0:26:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 看来练成了新的转弯技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:21.91,0:26:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全靠你的失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.75,0:26:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为失败是成功之母
